{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/gitlab-qq-email/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Fei"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8ebff12b-2f99-5cc7-8944-e274597bd3e0","excerpt":"安装 GitLab 作为代码托管服务，使用腾讯企业邮箱代发邮件。 安装 Omnibus Gitlab 链接 https://about.gitlab.com/downloads/ 配置 Omnibus Gitlab 打开配置文件 编辑配置文件 保存配置 应用配置","html":"<p>安装 GitLab 作为代码托管服务，使用腾讯企业邮箱代发邮件。</p>\n<h3>安装 Omnibus Gitlab</h3>\n<p>链接 <a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/downloads/\">https://about.gitlab.com/downloads/</a></p>\n<h3>配置 Omnibus Gitlab</h3>\n<p>打开配置文件</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">sudo vim /etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb</code></pre></div>\n<p>编辑配置文件</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"rb\"><pre class=\"language-rb\"><code class=\"language-rb\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 指定访问地址</span>\nexternal_url <span class=\"token string\">'http://192.168.1.100'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 配置腾讯企业邮箱账号</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_enable'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_address'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"smtp.exmail.qq.com\"</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_port'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_user_name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"邮箱地址\"</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_password'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"邮箱密码\"</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_domain'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"smtp.qq.com\"</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_authentication'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"login\"</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'smtp_enable_starttls_auto'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 指定发件人</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'gitlab_email_from'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"邮箱地址\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 调整时区</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'time_zone'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Asia/Shanghai'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 禁用Gravatar</span>\ngitlab_rails<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'gravatar_enabled'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>保存配置</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">:wq</code></pre></div>\n<p>应用配置</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">sudo gitlab-ctl reconfigure</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"GitLab配置腾讯企业邮箱","date":"2015-05-19","description":"如何使用 GitLab 托管代码，腾讯企业邮箱代码邮件？"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/gitlab-qq-email/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/setting-up-jshint/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"配置JSHint"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/migrate-from-ghost-to-hexo/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"从Ghost迁移到Hexo"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","4265873673"]}